Package: BiocChallengesTemplate
Title: Challenges for the Bioconductor community
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Kevin",
           family = "Rue-Albrecht",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "kevinrue67@gmail.com",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-3899-3872"))
Description: This package hosts thematic challenges contributed by and for the Bioconductor community.
    It imports core functionality implemented in the kevinrue/BiocChallenges repository, to manage, filter, and display challenges as articles of a pkgdown website.
    Challenges are bite-sized projects led by volunteers, encouraging collaboration and sharing of expertise between contributors.
